      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While some substances can have synergistic effects, combining alcohol and Zolpidem puts you at risk for dangerously intensified central nervous system depression. The receptors are sensitive, and even a small amount of alcohol can significantly alter how the medication works, leading to excessive sedation or respiratory issues. For optimal and safe sleep, stick strictly to the prescribed regimen without any alcohol interference. If you want a better sleep routine, discuss non-pharmacological aids with your physician.",
      "source": "target",
